Bluetongue, Spain
---------------
Information received on 4 Oct 2010 from Dr Lucio Ignacio Carbajo
Goni, Subdirector General de Sanidad de la Produccion Primaria,
Direccion General de Recursos Agricolas y Ganaderos, Ministerio de
Medio Ambiente y Medio Rural y Marino, Madrid, Spain

Summary
Report type: Immediate notification
Start date 6 Sep 2010
Date of 1st confirmation of the event 6 Sep 2010
Report date 1 Oct 2010
Date submitted to OIE 4 Oct 2010
Reason for notification Reoccurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence June 2009
Manifestation of disease: Sub-clinical infection
Causal agent: Bluetongue virus Serotype 4
Nature of diagnosis; Laboratory (advanced)
This event pertains to a defined zone within the country

New outbreaks
Outbreak 1 (1/2010) Vejer de la Frontera, ANDALUCIA
Date of start of the outbreak 6 Sep 2010
